{"id": 1172, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些原因让你去电影院看了一部烂片？", "description": "看到这么多过亿票房，还以为国产电影有救了呢。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5574, "comment_count": 31, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160822135946kB8rslyhYOu3ZDSI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-25T17:00:15Z", "questions": [{"id": 1057, "title": "哪些原因让你去电影院看了一部烂片？", "content": "哪些原因让你去电影院看了一部烂片？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 108256, "content": "被3D/IMAX的噱头吸引，结果剧情超弱", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145524goQfK671cRFsCEyu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108257, "content": "是片子里演员的脑残粉，就是去看一眼颜值", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145616STiGFuvkN16QAPOg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108258, "content": "这俩人同时出演？我可是他们的CP粉！", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145651S1zGRm8Y3XH2Zcyq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108259, "content": "很爱这部电影的原著，觉得据此改编的东西不会差吧", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145719ZaIkERQg71qeCBPX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108261, "content": "没看影评，随意买了张热门电影的票", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145742VmJHeI5386Myb0uk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108262, "content": "迷信豆瓣评分，结果影片上映的前两天都是水军", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145811Y2nTmsIQhBRNjzHv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108263, "content": "基友/对象非要去看", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145840dOsJHq3vw6SQAzME.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108264, "content": "整个电影院都没想看的，但朋友聚会没地方去", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145910R7LZtNzM9VrfB5WI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108265, "content": "为了歇脚或避雨，找个能坐上一阵子的地方", "image": "img/option/option/20160817145938UkcPL9fQJy4RVIe5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 108266, "content": "我知道它是烂片，就是为了吐槽专程去看的", "image": "img/option/option/20160817150006CXtDHL2Sh0vr8iWR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}